title: Joe & Tommy's Pack Of Lies - The National Skateboard Co.
description:
We're proud to present 'Joe & Tommy's Pack Of Lies' the newest video offering from the mighty good folk at The National Skateboard Co. This time TNSC treats us to two full parts from productive pair Joe Gavin and Tommy May filmed across the British Isles. If that wasn't enough there's cameos from team mates Don Irfan, Vaughan Jones, Dee Collins, Neil Smith, Victor Mputu and Zeta Rush. 

'Joe & Tommy's Pack Of Lies' was released to coincide with the drop of Joe Gavin's new 'Liquid Swords II' board.
 
Filmed by: Ryan Gray, Sean Lomax, Michal Busko, Sam Bottenberg & Mark Kendrick.
